{"name":"Discretix Technologies","permalink":"discretix-technologies","crunchbase_url":"http://www.crunchbase.com/company/discretix-technologies","homepage_url":"http://www.discretix.com/","blog_url":"","blog_feed_url":"","twitter_username":"trustembedded","category_code":"software","number_of_employees":null,"founded_year":2000,"founded_month":2,"founded_day":null,"deadpooled_year":null,"deadpooled_month":null,"deadpooled_day":null,"deadpooled_url":null,"tag_list":"","alias_list":"","email_address":"","phone_number":"972 7 32558800","description":"security platforms and solutions","created_at":"Tue Feb 16 10:34:05 UTC 2010","updated_at":"Fri Sep 07 11:35:51 UTC 2012","overview":"<p>Discretix Technologies Ltd. develops embedded security platforms and solutions for mobile and flash memory devices in Israel. Its technology incorporates security at the chipset level, as well as protects sensitive information and applications from malicious attacks, viruses, fraud, and theft. The company offers CryptoCell, a security solution to mobile handset and chipset manufacturers, which equips handsets, Smartphones, PDAs, and multimedia devices with device and content protection against various threats; and CryptoFlash, a security platform for flash based portable and embedded memory devices, such as flash cards, USB flash drives, embedded flash memory, high capacity SIM cards, and hard disk drives. It also provides Multi-Scheme DRM Client, a software solution that protects the distribution and consumption of premium content on mobile devices; Multi-Scheme MobileTV Security Client, which secures the distribution and consumption of mobile TV; and middleware and toolkits that protects sensitive information, such as device and user credentials, and e-commerce data from unauthorized access, while allowing access to the underlying cryptographic libraries. The company serves semiconductor and device manufacturers. </p>\n\n<p>Discretix Technologies Ltd. was founded in 2000 and is headqua